

UC Davis Mens Volleyball is a UCD Intramural Sports & Sport Clubs club sport at UC Davis.  Established in 1967 by Gary Colberg, the club has  become one of the premier volleyball clubs in the nation. The club is actually twotiered, supporting Varsity I and Varsity II teams.  Representing the highly competitive Northern California Collegiate Volleyball League, both the Davis Varsity I and II teams have consistently proven themselves to be top10 national finishers within the NIRSA club volleyball rankings.

